snippet.title: Motor Mash - PlayStation Gameplay (Steam/GOG Re-Release)
snippet.description:
This PAL-exclusive game got a re-release on Steam. In case you want to hear my thoughts on it, have a look at my InfiniteBacklog review.

https://infinitebacklog.nl/users/aklim95/reviews/motor-mash

Motor Mash (C) Piko Interactive
Originally developed by Eutechnyx
Steam store page: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1257950/Motor_Mash/
GOG.com page: https://www.gog.com/en/game/motor_mash
